title.rendered: Alticor Inc Completes First Project at Marine Corps Base Hawaii

content.rendered: Alticor Inc is proud to announce the completion of P-864 MALS 24 Aircraft Maintenance Expansion, its first project at Marine Corps Base Hawaii. MALS 24 is a design-build project awarded to FTSI/Phelps Joint Venture. The project is a composite shop that consists of administrative offices, industrial work areas and a large paint booth and warehouse space for all aircraft part maintenance.
